note: Based around Brisbane and the Sunshine Coast, I present an ever-expanding catalogue of rootsy, country, backwoods, and urban folk tales from an Australian point of view. Generally narrative in style, they are tales about the land, of our indigenous people, train songs, cowboy songs, city songs, drug songs, blues, instrumentals; songs unique to things Australian... but elsewhere too. Because there's a a touch of Americana here and there... from the dark side of the hills....
